me. The death penalty remains a deadly political tool in most of the United States."--Publisher's description.  a16 0aCapital punishmentzUnited StatesxHistory.  aHV 8699 U5 L96 2015c1hUAAU-Bi0162035232071  aHV 8699 U5 L96 2015wLCc1i0162034578367d2/12/2015e2/9/2015lON_SHELFmUAAUGn1p$150.00rYsYtBOOKu2/4/201501ahttp://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n85306933bhttp://viaf.org/viaf/75309017